stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Draft
  Draft --> Issued: Issue only if Ready

  state Draft {
    [*] --> NotReady
    NotReady --> Ready: Valid draft minimum met
    Ready --> NotReady: Missing required context or blocking error
  }

  state "Signals - orthogonal" as SIG {
    [*] --> None
    None --> NeedsReview
    NeedsReview --> None
    None --> Stale
    Stale --> None
  }

  note right of Issued
    Issued is document truth snapshot.
    Downstream Paid or Overdue lives in Receivables and Cash contexts.
  end note
